20namespace webrtc {
21
22absl::optional<AudioDecoderL16::Config> AudioDecoderL16::SdpToConfig(
23 const SdpAudioFormat& format) {
24 Config config;
25 config.sample_rate_hz = format.clockrate_hz;
26 config.num_channels = rtc::checked_cast<int>(format.num_channels);
27 return absl::EqualsIgnoreCase(format.name, "L16") && config.IsOk()
28 ? absl::optional<Config>(config)
29 : absl::nullopt;
30}
31
32void AudioDecoderL16::AppendSupportedDecoders(
33 std::vector<AudioCodecSpec>* specs) {
34 Pcm16BAppendSupportedCodecSpecs(specs);
35}
36
37std::unique_ptr<AudioDecoder> AudioDecoderL16::MakeAudioDecoder(
38 const Config& config,
39 absl::optional<AudioCodecPairId> /*codec_pair_id*/) {
40 return config.IsOk() ? std::make_unique<AudioDecoderPcm16B>(
41 config.sample_rate_hz, config.num_channels)
42 : nullptr;
43}
